For more information see:
http://jkaltes.byethost16.com/Juggluco/cmdline/index.html

Compile for debugging with:

cmake -DDEBUG=ON $srcdir
make juggluco

To compile without logging and debug information (in a fresh directory):

cmake $srcdir
make juggluco


To try out the ssl version of the xdrip server add -DSSLXDRIP=ON to cmake. For example:

cmake  -DSSLXDRIP=ON $srcdir

